## 🌟 What Makes CineScope Special  

CineScope isn’t just another movie app — it’s a **personal AI-powered companion** that learns your taste, mood, and habits to recommend movies you’ll truly love.  

### 🎥 Cinematic Experience  
- Epic movie trailers as live backgrounds  
- Automatic trailer rotation for freshness  
- Interactive overlays & controls  

### 🧠 AI Personality Engine  
- Custom-built AI (no external APIs)  
- Psychological profiling & mood analysis  
- 6 unique personality types (Explorer, Connector, Analyst, Dreamer, etc.)  

### 🎯 Smart Recommendations  
- Mood-sensitive picks  
- Complexity-matched suggestions  
- Fresh & varied discovery  

---

## ✨ Core Features  

- 🔮 **AI Discovery**: Personality quiz, evolving taste learning  
- 🎬 **Cinematic Search**: Instant search, watchlist, reviews  
- 👥 **Social (Coming Soon)**: Taste matching, friend recs, safe community reviews  
- 🛡️ **Privacy First**: No external AI, spoiler protection, secure data  

---

## 🚀 Tech Stack  

**Frontend**  
- Next.js 14 · TypeScript 5 · Tailwind CSS · Framer Motion  

**Backend**  
- PostgreSQL · Prisma · NextAuth.js  

**AI & Data**  
- Custom AI Engine · TMDB API  

---

## 🛠️ Getting Started  

### 📋 Prerequisites  
- Node.js 18+  
- PostgreSQL database  

### ⚡ Installation  
```bash
git clone https://github.com/teddexter0/cinescope.git
cd cinescope
npm install
